22static inline isc_result_t
23fromtext_rp(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
24 isc_token_t token;
25 dns_name_t name;
26 isc_buffer_t buffer;
27 int i;
28 bool ok;
29
30 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
31
32 UNUSED(type);
33 UNUSED(rdclass);
34 UNUSED(callbacks);
35
36 if (origin == NULL)
37 origin = dns_rootname;
38
39 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
40 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
41 isc_tokentype_string,
42 false));
43 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
44 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
45 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin,
46 options, target));
47 ok = true;
48 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0 && i == 0)
49 ok = dns_name_ismailbox(&name);
50 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
51 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
52 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
53 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
54 }
55 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
56}
57
58static inline isc_result_t
59totext_rp(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
60 isc_region_t region;
61 dns_name_t rmail;
62 dns_name_t email;
63 dns_name_t prefix;
64 bool sub;
65
66 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
67 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
68
69 dns_name_init(&rmail, NULL);
70 dns_name_init(&email, NULL);
71 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
72
73 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
74
75 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
76 isc_region_consume(&region, rmail.length);
77
78 dns_name_fromregion(&email, &region);
79 isc_region_consume(&region, email.length);
80
81 sub = name_prefix(&rmail, tctx->origin, &prefix);
82 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
83
84 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
85
86 sub = name_prefix(&email, tctx->origin, &prefix);
87 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
88}

90static inline isc_result_t
91fromwire_rp(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
92 dns_name_t rmail;
93 dns_name_t email;
94
95 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
96
97 UNUSED(type);
98 UNUSED(rdclass);
99
100 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
101
102 dns_name_init(&rmail, NULL);
103 dns_name_init(&email, NULL);
104
105 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&rmail, source, dctx, options, target));
106 return (dns_name_fromwire(&email, source, dctx, options, target));
107}
108
109static inline isc_result_t
110towire_rp(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
111 isc_region_t region;
112 dns_name_t rmail;
113 dns_name_t email;
114 dns_offsets_t roffsets;
115 dns_offsets_t eoffsets;
116
117 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
118 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
119
120 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
121 dns_name_init(&rmail, roffsets);
122 dns_name_init(&email, eoffsets);
123
124 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
125
126 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
127 isc_region_consume(&region, rmail.length);
128
129 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&rmail, cctx, target));
130
131 dns_name_fromregion(&rmail, &region);
132 isc_region_consume(&region, rmail.length);
133
134 return (dns_name_towire(&rmail, cctx, target));
135}

137static inline int
138compare_rp(ARGS_COMPARE) {
139 isc_region_t region1;
140 isc_region_t region2;
141 dns_name_t name1;
142 dns_name_t name2;
143 int order;
144
145 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
146 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
147 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
148 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
149 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
150
151 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
152 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
153
154 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
155 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
156
157 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
158 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
159
160 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
161 if (order != 0)
162 return (order);
163
164 isc_region_consume(&region1, name_length(&name1));
165 isc_region_consume(&region2, name_length(&name2));
166
167 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
168 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
169
170 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
171 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
172
173 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
174}

176static inline isc_result_t
177fromstruct_rp(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
178 dns_rdata_rp_t *rp = source;
179 isc_region_t region;
180
181 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
182 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
183 REQUIRE(rp->common.rdtype == type);
184 REQUIRE(rp->common.rdclass == rdclass);
185
186 UNUSED(type);
187 UNUSED(rdclass);
188
189 dns_name_toregion(&rp->mail, &region);
190 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
191 dns_name_toregion(&rp->text, &region);
192 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
193}
194
195static inline isc_result_t
196tostruct_rp(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
197 isc_result_t result;
198 isc_region_t region;
199 dns_rdata_rp_t *rp = target;
200 dns_name_t name;
201
202 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
203 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
204 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
205
206 rp->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
207 rp->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
208 ISC_LINK_INIT(&rp->common, link);
209
210 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
211 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
212 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
213 dns_name_init(&rp->mail, NULL);
214 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &rp->mail));
215 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
216 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
217 dns_name_init(&rp->text, NULL);
218 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &rp->text);
219 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
220 goto cleanup;
221
222 rp->mctx = mctx;
223 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
224
225 cleanup:
226 if (mctx != NULL)
227 dns_name_free(&rp->mail, mctx);
228 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
229}
230
231static inline void
232freestruct_rp(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
233 dns_rdata_rp_t *rp = source;
234
235 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
236 REQUIRE(rp->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_rp);
237
238 if (rp->mctx == NULL)
239 return;
240
241 dns_name_free(&rp->mail, rp->mctx);
242 dns_name_free(&rp->text, rp->mctx);
243 rp->mctx = NULL;
244}

246static inline isc_result_t
247additionaldata_rp(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
248 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
249
250 UNUSED(rdata);
251 UNUSED(add);
252 UNUSED(arg);
253
254 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
255}

257static inline isc_result_t
258digest_rp(ARGS_DIGEST) {
259 isc_region_t r;
260 dns_name_t name;
261
262 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
263
264 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
265 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
266
267 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
268 RETERR(dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
269 isc_region_consume(&r, name_length(&name));
270
271 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
272 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
273
274 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
275}

277static inline bool
278checkowner_rp(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
279
280 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
281
282 UNUSED(name);
283 UNUSED(type);
284 UNUSED(rdclass);
285 UNUSED(wildcard);
286
287 return (true);
288}
289
290static inline bool
291checknames_rp(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
292 isc_region_t region;
293 dns_name_t name;
294
295 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_rp);
296
297 UNUSED(owner);
298
299 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
300 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
301 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
302 if (!dns_name_ismailbox(&name)) {
303 if (bad != NULL)
304 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
305 return (false);
306 }
307 return (true);
308}
309
310static inline int
311casecompare_rp(ARGS_COMPARE) {
312 return (compare_rp(rdata1, rdata2));
313}
